p.k: Drama, Mystery Usa (2014). Hrají: Lindsay Burdge, Jennifer Lafleur, Aleksa Palladino. Režie: Sarah Adina Smith.
p.d: Spirit Lake is unusually deep. No diver has ever managed to find the bottom, though many have tried. When Dr. Amelia Brooks disappears during a deep-water dive, her three daughters travel home to settle her affairs. They find themselves unable to let go of their mother and become drawn into the mysteries of the lake.
